trailingComments.value: * * Drops the first n values of the input iterable. * * @example * // returns [ 3 , 4 ] * list( _drop( range( 5 ) , 3 ) ) ; * * @param {Iterable} iterable - The input iterable. * @param {Number} n - The nonnegative number of values to drop. * @returns {IterableIterator} - The remaining values of the input iterable.
